text: Eat Your Heart Out is an Australian rock band formed in Newcastle in 2012. After playing in the Snake Or Die Tour in 2016, they signed to label Fearless Records in 2017 and headlined their own Carried Away Tour. In 2018 they toured with Movements, whose member Patrick Miranda has also collaborated with the band on the tracks "Conscience" and "Carousel". ==Members== * Caitlin Henry – Vocals * Andrew Anderson – Guitar * Will Moore – Guitar * Dom Cant – Bass * Jake Cronin – Drums ==Discography== ===Albums=== *Florescence (2019), under Fearless Records ===EPs=== *Distance Between Us (2015) *Carried Away (2017), under Fearless Records *Mind Games (2017), under Fearless Records ===Singles=== *"Carousel" (2019), on Florescence *"Spinning" (2019), on Florescence *"Closer to the Sun" (2019), on Florescence ==References== Category:Musical quintets Category:Musical groups established in 2012 Category:Australian grunge groups Category:New South Wales musical groups Category:Newcastle, New South Wales Category:Australian alternative metal musical groups Category:Living people Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
